 - min 2.5 MB free other memory
 - Workbench 3.0
 - Harddisk (min.3 MB frei)

 !!! The program also works with a smaller amount of memory, but for !!!
 !!! the Video-Animation you need it, so if you have not enough      !!!
 !!! memory the program will quit.                                   !!!
@ENDNODE

